  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0d85\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0db4\u0dad\u0da7 \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0dc1\u0dda\u0dc2\u0dba \u0daf\u0dd0\u0db1\u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd3\u0db8\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "To know the fuel balance of the fuel pass",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A system has been introduced to inform those registered for the National Fuel Permit about their fuel quota balance.",
        "There it is possible to know the balance by typing FUEL BAL as your vehicle number (eg ABC 1234) and sending an SMS message to the phone number 0766 220 000.",
        "To get the National Fuel Pass, you can visit the website www.fuelpass.gov.lk and do the relevant registration."
      ],
